  "title": "Lasting Power of Attorney",
  "strapline": "Service dashboard",
  "tagline": "Figures for the service to make a <strong>lasting power of attorney (LPA)</strong> â€“ a legal document that lets you appoint someone, known as an 'attorney', to make decisions on your behalf. Figures include applications made via both digital and paper form channels.",
